hopobject.body: Languages finaflex revolution test stack supplements He fouled up, he accepts, and he reckons he deserved to pay for his disgrace, stripped of a world time trial championship and with reputation forever shredded. There is not a day, he says, when he does not regret the path he took, even if he felt there was a silver lining in how his downfall enabled him to “reboot” his life as it seemed to be tumbling into calamitous freefall.
